item.title: CVE-2023-5089|2024-08-02T07:44:53.860Z -- unknown -- defender%20security
item.description: The Defender Security WordPress plugin before 4.1.0 does not prevent redirects to the login page via the auth_redirect WordPress function, allowing an unauthenticated visitor to access the login page, even when the hide login page functionality of the plugin is enabled.
